# index.json is a GENERATED artifact — the designer dev-server plugin
# regenerates it from a fresh scan on every write. It mutates (timestamps) on
# every dev-server GET and would create constant churn, so it is not committed.
# The CLI (`ribbonflow build`) also builds its own index from a fresh scan.
index.json

# Throwaway flow-sets the designer Playwright e2e seeds + tears down
# (imperative-renderer.spec.js → smoke-e2e/, authoring-ux.spec.js → zz-pw-authoring/).
# Gitignored so a server-backed e2e run never dirties the working tree.
smoke-e2e/
zz-pw-authoring/
